## Risks
- SSL Verification: If the app checks SSL, this will fail. We might need to edit `hosts` file instead (mapping `hoanphicrypto.com` -> `127.0.0.1`) AND run a local HTTPS server with a self-signed cert (requires trusting cert).
- **First Step:** Try Proxy. If fails, try Hosts file modification.
